,Recommended,238320,24209089,"Posted: 9 July, 2016",all,みoƦƦoƦ ₣o父,"Hey everyone and this is my review about the game!This is a Horror Parkour survival puzzle game.Interface/Menu/SettingsThere are some Resolution sizes.You can play this game in Fullscreen mode or Windowed mode.There is only a Volume Slidebar.There is a Sensitivity Slidebar.There are many languages available.Able to turn on Subtitles.Able to change your Gamma (Brightness).You are able to change the controls on your keyboard.You are able to play with your controller and with RUMBLE FUNCTION!You can choose between 3 Pre-sets of controller controls.There is 4 difficulty settings. (From Normal to insane)About the game.You are a journalist investigating a crazy psychaotic Mansion. You have to try to find secrets and clues to reveal, why everything is behaving so weird lately. You have a video camera with you, to record and have vision in the dark area. You have no weapons and you are only able to Run and hide from enemies. You have to find batteries from time to time to refill the camera's light vision. You will have to jump/squeeze through and doing other obstactles and puzzle to complete your path. It is not required to find every collectable, unless you are doing it for an achievement ofcourse. Collectables do tell you abit more information about the story. There are alot of puzzles to complete or you have to go to a certain location and activate this to activate that. and so go on. Do make sure you close the doors behind you, to slow down the enemies. However they might destroy the door instead.Great Dark atmosphere.Great soundtrack.Music/Sound changes whenever an enemy sees you or is nearby.Deep and maybe interesting Story.You can zoom in and out with your camera to see incoming enemies or area's.Your health Regenerate overtime.Enemies have sometimes Night vision eyes.Enemies walk and wander ALWAYS around your area.Has many (Different) collectables.Has nudity.Has Chapter Selection. (There are 8 Chapters).Has some Jumpscares but mainly the scariness is building up.Other things.Enemies are trying to find you if you are hiding. Stupidly enough they are not checking everything even if there is just a locker next to him. He will only check one thing and then he leaves the room even if the room is Dead-end.Make sure that you always hide if you have activated something. Enemies will always check out the ""activated"" item.Im always surprised that enemies can't hear the extreme breathing sound from the character.-------------------I Give this game a 8/10"
